1
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:29,792
=Lost You Forever S2=

2
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:32,784
=Episode 7=

3
00:01:36,010 --> 00:01:37,529
Has Skinny ever disliked you?

4
00:01:38,329 --> 00:01:40,289
Have you ever had regrets or grievances?

5
00:01:43,249 --> 00:01:46,370
I'm not a prostitute,
and he's not my client.

6
00:01:46,569 --> 00:01:50,490
Life can't always be sweet.

7
00:01:50,849 --> 00:01:52,569
Sometimes, it's also bitter.

8
00:01:54,649 --> 00:01:57,810
After I gave birth to two sons,

9
00:01:59,329 --> 00:02:01,690
I almost split up with Skinny.

10
00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:04,329
However,

11
00:02:04,569 --> 00:02:07,130
Skinny begged me

12
00:02:07,329 --> 00:02:08,209
and apologized.

13
00:02:10,209 --> 00:02:13,330
So, I forgave him.

14
00:02:16,890 --> 00:02:19,090
When I look back and think about it,

15
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,769
I feel lucky

16
00:02:22,289 --> 00:02:25,010
that I didn't break up with him.

17
00:02:28,489 --> 00:02:30,289
It seems time has ultimately proven

18
00:02:31,289 --> 00:02:33,610
that your choice was not wrong.

19
00:02:36,849 --> 00:02:39,129
In my life,

20
00:02:41,090 --> 00:02:43,929
I've cried, laughed,

21
00:02:45,569 --> 00:02:48,530
and tasted bitterness and sweetness.

22
00:02:51,610 --> 00:02:52,489
It's been worth it.

23
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:56,049
It's been worth it.

24
00:02:58,569 --> 00:03:01,010
But people can only see the choice
in front of them,

25
00:03:02,010 --> 00:03:03,330
not in the future.

26
00:03:05,289 --> 00:03:07,409
What if we make a choice right now

27
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:10,010
that makes us sad,

28
00:03:10,849 --> 00:03:12,450
but we won't regret it in the future?

29
00:03:13,090 --> 00:03:14,929
About this question,

30
00:03:15,370 --> 00:03:17,569
I can't answer it.

31
00:03:18,250 --> 00:03:19,370
Even those deities

32
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:21,730
who've lived for hundreds of years

33
00:03:22,209 --> 00:03:24,049
can't answer it either.

34
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:27,769
Living a life is

35
00:03:28,769 --> 00:03:33,450
like making a journey in the wilderness.

36
00:03:34,209 --> 00:03:38,489
Nobody knows what lies ahead.

37
00:03:40,610 --> 00:03:44,330
Perhaps it's smooth.

38
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:47,010
Or perhaps,

39
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:50,129
it's a bumpy road.

40
00:03:51,890 --> 00:03:52,929
So,

41
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:56,289
everyone wants to find a companion

42
00:03:58,450 --> 00:04:02,409
to support each other.

43
00:04:02,849 --> 00:04:04,530
Life is full of challenges,

44
00:04:04,769 --> 00:04:06,649
obstacles, and setbacks,

45
00:04:07,849 --> 00:04:11,010
but we try to live our lives.

46
00:04:11,330 --> 00:04:12,970
What if you choose

47
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:15,489
and trust the wrong person?

48
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:18,249
Young lady.

49
00:04:18,809 --> 00:04:19,849
Just remember

50
00:04:21,330 --> 00:04:22,969
that if you want something,

51
00:04:23,689 --> 00:04:24,650
you must believe

52
00:04:24,650 --> 00:04:26,930
that it exists.

53
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:29,170
If you refuse

54
00:04:29,450 --> 00:04:31,249
to believe,

55
00:04:31,650 --> 00:04:33,730
you won't give your heart.

56
00:04:35,529 --> 00:04:38,610
If you don't even give your heart,

57
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:41,650
you won't

58
00:04:41,849 --> 00:04:44,129
get what you want at all.

59
00:04:47,129 --> 00:04:47,849
(If I don't believe)

60
00:04:48,289 --> 00:04:49,010
(and give,)

61
00:04:50,010 --> 00:04:51,809
(I won't get what I want.)

62
00:04:53,249 --> 00:04:55,809
(Jing and I have come to this.)

63
00:04:56,969 --> 00:04:58,249
(Could it be my fault?)

64
00:05:26,050 --> 00:05:26,809
Tian'er.

65
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:30,569
You've done well.

66
00:05:32,129 --> 00:05:33,450
Skinny must feel lucky

67
00:05:33,849 --> 00:05:36,010
to marry a good wife.

68
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:39,730
Mu

69
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:41,849
and I are happy for you.

70
00:05:46,050 --> 00:05:48,730
Who are you?

71
00:06:24,490 --> 00:06:25,770
Xiaoliu.

72
00:07:12,089 --> 00:07:13,450
This place hasn't changed.

73
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:14,969
Sadly, you and I

74
00:07:15,369 --> 00:07:17,409
can no longer get along as we used to.

75
00:07:19,890 --> 00:07:21,330
You are the Princess of Haoling.

76
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:23,089
I am a rebel general.

77
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:25,369
We live in different worlds.

78
00:07:26,210 --> 00:07:27,170
No need to feel sad.

79
00:07:29,569 --> 00:07:30,529
You're right.

80
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:33,890
We are from different worlds.

81
00:07:38,930 --> 00:07:40,689
I've been missing for so long.

82
00:07:41,249 --> 00:07:42,650
There must be an uproar out there.

83
00:07:48,129 --> 00:07:49,330
You did this.

84
00:07:50,369 --> 00:07:52,050
Yet the Fangfeng Family
has to take the blame.

85
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:54,969
Fangfeng Yiying will have to shield them

86
00:07:54,969 --> 00:07:56,330
from this unexpected disaster.

87
00:07:57,289 --> 00:07:59,249
She is Chief Tushan's wife.

88
00:08:00,129 --> 00:08:01,890
So she will
get the Tushan Family involved.

89
00:08:06,890 --> 00:08:09,050
You think I'm the one
who wants to ruin your wedding?

90
00:08:15,409 --> 00:08:16,289
If it's not you, who then?

91
00:08:21,289 --> 00:08:22,689
I have a deal to do with you.

92
00:08:23,490 --> 00:08:24,129
I need you

93
00:08:24,289 --> 00:08:25,730
to stop Fenglong's wedding with Xiaoyao.

94
00:08:26,210 --> 00:08:28,089
In what capacity do you ask for my help?

95
00:08:29,010 --> 00:08:29,650
Ye Shiqi?

96
00:08:31,450 --> 00:08:32,729
Can he afford my help?

97
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:34,129
Ye Shiqi can't afford it,

98
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,290
but Tushan Jing can.

99
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:37,249
Tushan Jing?

100
00:08:38,929 --> 00:08:40,809
Who is he to stop this wedding?

101
00:08:41,249 --> 00:08:42,210
I pay for a service.

102
00:08:42,850 --> 00:08:43,850
You get paid to do a job.

103
00:08:45,129 --> 00:08:46,410
Since when do you care who I am

104
00:08:46,410 --> 00:08:47,369
when doing business?

105
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:56,850
Help me stop this wedding.

106
00:08:57,929 --> 00:08:58,809
From now on,

107
00:08:59,249 --> 00:09:01,489
I will provide provisions
for the Chenrong Army every year.

108
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:02,929
This seal is the proof.

109
00:09:03,290 --> 00:09:04,970
Money is a good thing.

110
00:09:05,210 --> 00:09:06,809
You can hire others

111
00:09:08,129 --> 00:09:09,249
to do what you dare not to do.

112
00:09:10,129 --> 00:09:10,929
Chief Tushan.

113
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:12,809
That's very generous.

114
00:09:13,090 --> 00:09:14,569
Will you take this deal or not?

115
00:09:14,569 --> 00:09:15,248
I'll take it.

116
00:09:15,489 --> 00:09:16,330
Why not?

117
00:09:18,530 --> 00:09:19,369
You know,

118
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:21,609
I never turn down money.

119
00:09:21,970 --> 00:09:22,544
Good.

120
00:09:22,689 --> 00:09:24,609
I hope you can stop it
before the wedding.

121
00:09:25,410 --> 00:09:26,489
Don't disturb others.

122
00:09:27,410 --> 00:09:28,530
Minimize the harm.

123
00:09:28,609 --> 00:09:29,770
I've taken the deal.

124
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:32,569
I decide how to finish this.

125
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:34,410
You needn't bother.

126
00:09:38,369 --> 00:09:40,049
I don't need you to tell me what to do

127
00:09:40,249 --> 00:09:41,489
or set the price.

128
00:09:42,530 --> 00:09:44,049
I decide how you're going

129
00:09:44,049 --> 00:09:44,970
to pay for my help.

130
00:09:45,569 --> 00:09:46,290
My word is final.

131
00:09:47,090 --> 00:09:48,049
I help you ruin the wedding,

132
00:09:48,530 --> 00:09:51,169
and you provide the Chenrong Army
with army provisions

133
00:09:52,489 --> 00:09:53,890
for 37 years.

134
00:09:54,210 --> 00:09:56,090
Tushan Jing hired you to do that?

135
00:09:58,330 --> 00:09:59,330
If you don't believe it,

136
00:09:59,970 --> 00:10:01,210
you can ask Tushan Jing yourself.

137
00:10:03,090 --> 00:10:04,609
By what right did he ruin my wedding?

138
00:10:05,569 --> 00:10:06,410
What does he want?

139
00:10:07,049 --> 00:10:08,290
I was hired to do a job.

140
00:10:09,249 --> 00:10:10,129
What the employer thinks

141
00:10:10,689 --> 00:10:11,569
is none of my concern.

142
00:10:17,369 --> 00:10:18,210
I hate him.

143
00:10:19,929 --> 00:10:20,809
When can I leave?

144
00:10:22,450 --> 00:10:23,970
I've already got what I wanted.

145
00:10:24,410 --> 00:10:25,169
You can leave

146
00:10:25,929 --> 00:10:26,450
at any time.

147
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,410
Just a reminder,

148
00:10:34,129 --> 00:10:35,568
the poisonous bug isn't removed.

149
00:10:37,890 --> 00:10:39,970
If you reveal that I'm Fangfeng Bei,

150
00:10:41,290 --> 00:10:43,410
I will give you a painful death.

151
00:10:51,169 --> 00:10:52,090
You don't believe it?

152
00:11:07,650 --> 00:11:08,569
If you don't want to die,

153
00:11:09,809 --> 00:11:11,609
don't say anything you shouldn't.

154
00:11:16,530 --> 00:11:17,210
Is this

155
00:11:19,090 --> 00:11:22,650
why you won't remove the poisonous bug?

156
00:11:23,929 --> 00:11:25,049
General Xiang Liu.

157
00:11:26,010 --> 00:11:27,010
What a scheming one.

158
00:11:31,249 --> 00:11:32,609
This is the kind of person I am.

159
00:11:34,249 --> 00:11:35,729
You knew it.

160
00:12:50,890 --> 00:12:51,609
Mr. Yu.

161
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:03,049
Yu Xin.

162
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:04,609
Watch your manners.

163
00:13:07,169 --> 00:13:08,010
Miss.

164
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:08,890
Are you looking for me?

165
00:13:09,609 --> 00:13:10,569
I want to see Tushan Jing.

166
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:11,929
Take me to Qingqiu.

167
00:13:13,929 --> 00:13:15,290
Who do you think you are

168
00:13:15,330 --> 00:13:17,049
to see Chief Tushan?

169
00:13:17,090 --> 00:13:18,330
Tushan Jing will definitely see me.

170
00:13:19,049 --> 00:13:20,090
If I'm lying,

171
00:13:20,530 --> 00:13:21,609
you'll just make a trip in vain.

172
00:13:22,290 --> 00:13:23,450
After all, I am in your hands.

173
00:13:23,689 --> 00:13:24,569
You can punish me.

174
00:13:24,809 --> 00:13:26,330
If I'm not lying,

175
00:13:26,729 --> 00:13:27,770
but you refuse me,

176
00:13:28,210 --> 00:13:30,410
you will make a big mistake.

177
00:13:40,169 --> 00:13:41,689
You don't look like an ordinary lady.

178
00:13:42,129 --> 00:13:43,770
I don't think you're lying.

179
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:47,729
I will accompany you to Qingqiu.

180
00:13:51,636 --> 00:13:53,584
(Qingshui Town)

181
00:14:01,169 --> 00:14:01,744
Miss.

182
00:14:02,210 --> 00:14:03,369
After leaving Qingshui Town

183
00:14:03,450 --> 00:14:04,489
and the snow abates,

184
00:14:04,650 --> 00:14:05,609
we'll take a cloud carriage.

185
00:14:06,249 --> 00:14:06,832
Okay.

186
00:14:22,129 --> 00:14:23,569
(I'm afraid of loneliness.)

187
00:14:23,569 --> 00:14:25,049
(If I can't find
enduring companionship,)

188
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:26,729
(a brief encounter is also good.)

189
00:14:37,169 --> 00:14:39,489
(Fangfeng Bei,
who accompanied you briefly, has died.)

190
00:14:40,609 --> 00:14:42,530
(You can now enjoy someone else's
enduring company.)

191
00:15:32,692 --> 00:15:35,600
(Tushan Mansion)

192
00:15:38,929 --> 00:15:40,049
She wants to see the Chief.

193
00:15:40,210 --> 00:15:41,450
So you brought her here?

194
00:15:41,689 --> 00:15:43,249
How could you act so rashly?

195
00:15:44,729 --> 00:15:45,290
It is her.

196
00:16:00,249 --> 00:16:00,890
Jing Ye.

197
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:04,080
Prin...

198
00:16:05,249 --> 00:16:05,890
Princess?

199
00:16:26,850 --> 00:16:29,090
This pill only relieves your heartache.

200
00:16:29,330 --> 00:16:30,249
But it can't cure you.

201
00:16:30,770 --> 00:16:31,650
Your heart is damaged.

202
00:16:32,169 --> 00:16:33,330
Don't think or worry too much.

203
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:34,450
You need some quiet rest.

204
00:16:35,609 --> 00:16:36,176
Okay.

205
00:16:37,249 --> 00:16:38,049
I got it.

206
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:40,689
I know

207
00:16:41,290 --> 00:16:43,049
you're worried about someone.

208
00:16:43,729 --> 00:16:44,650
You can't stop worrying.

209
00:16:47,169 --> 00:16:47,770
Chief.

210
00:16:48,049 --> 00:16:49,729
The princess is here.

211
00:16:59,129 --> 00:16:59,760
Jing Ye.

212
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:00,809
Get new clothes for me.

213
00:17:01,090 --> 00:17:02,169
I smell of medicine.

214
00:17:03,249 --> 00:17:04,369
How do I look?

215
00:17:04,449 --> 00:17:05,930
You look much better.

216
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:08,530
The princess is weary from her trip.

217
00:17:08,609 --> 00:17:09,489
I have arranged for a maid

218
00:17:09,489 --> 00:17:11,010
to help the princess get bathed
and dressed.

219
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:12,489
It will take a while.

220
00:17:13,050 --> 00:17:13,890
Chief, no rush.

221
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:14,849
Take your time.

222
00:17:29,249 --> 00:17:30,170
No need to sweep it.

223
00:17:30,930 --> 00:17:32,129
The princess likes the snow.

224
00:17:33,609 --> 00:17:34,129
Your Majesty.

225
00:17:34,969 --> 00:17:36,050
The princess hasn't returned.

226
00:17:36,570 --> 00:17:37,449
The snow...

227
00:17:38,050 --> 00:17:39,089
Xiaoyao will come back.

228
00:17:39,329 --> 00:17:40,449
No matter where she is,

229
00:17:41,890 --> 00:17:43,170
I will find her and bring her back.

230
00:17:43,489 --> 00:17:44,080
Okay.

231
00:17:44,890 --> 00:17:45,810
Keep the snow

232
00:17:46,449 --> 00:17:47,449
until the princess returns.

233
00:17:51,410 --> 00:17:54,530
This year's winter is unusually cold.

234
00:17:54,849 --> 00:17:55,729
It's the same every year.

235
00:17:56,170 --> 00:17:57,329
Every year around this time,

236
00:17:57,530 --> 00:17:59,489
it snows frequently.

237
00:17:59,930 --> 00:18:01,290
In previous years, with Xiaoyao around,

238
00:18:02,170 --> 00:18:03,089
even when it snowed,

239
00:18:04,329 --> 00:18:05,010
I didn't feel cold.

240
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,449
The princess loved the snow.

241
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:09,249
At Zhaoyun Peak,

242
00:18:09,369 --> 00:18:10,369
whenever it snowed,

243
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:11,609
the princess would be happy.

244
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:14,890
It's always spring in Haoling.

245
00:18:16,690 --> 00:18:18,369
Xiaoyao never saw snow before.

246
00:18:19,609 --> 00:18:20,810
Naturally, she's happy

247
00:18:22,050 --> 00:18:22,849
to see the snow.

248
00:18:50,690 --> 00:18:52,050
Your Majesty used to do this

249
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:53,329
to please the princess.

250
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:55,209
You're drawing me.

251
00:18:57,690 --> 00:18:59,249
It was easy to cheer her up
when she was a kid.

252
00:19:00,209 --> 00:19:01,650
Her emotions always appeared
on her face.

253
00:19:03,849 --> 00:19:04,570
If I pleased her,

254
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:07,129
she would be very happy.

255
00:19:25,729 --> 00:19:26,320
(Forget it.)

256
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:28,290
(What can I do even if I ask him?)

257
00:19:29,170 --> 00:19:31,010
(Even though Tushan Jing is behind it,)

258
00:19:31,530 --> 00:19:32,690
(can I kill him?)

259
00:19:34,249 --> 00:19:35,810
(It's just going to bother me.)

260
00:19:38,930 --> 00:19:39,890
(I'd better leave.)

261
00:19:58,650 --> 00:19:59,369
Thank you.

262
00:20:09,729 --> 00:20:11,570
I came here
in a fit of anger because of Xiang Liu.

263
00:20:12,729 --> 00:20:13,570
You know,

264
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:15,369
people tend to be impulsive
when they are angry.

265
00:20:16,129 --> 00:20:17,410
When I'm impulsive,

266
00:20:17,810 --> 00:20:19,410
I'll do something I don't want to.

267
00:20:21,170 --> 00:20:23,089
Actually, I didn't intend to see you.

268
00:20:24,089 --> 00:20:24,849
I just...

269
00:20:26,010 --> 00:20:26,930
It's getting late.

270
00:20:28,089 --> 00:20:29,290
There might be a blizzard.

271
00:20:29,969 --> 00:20:30,770
You stay for the night.

272
00:20:31,050 --> 00:20:33,010
Tomorrow morning, I'll send you
back to Chenrong Mountain.

273
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:36,810
It doesn't look like
it's going to snow again.

274
00:20:40,329 --> 00:20:40,849
Look.

275
00:20:41,969 --> 00:20:43,050
The weather wants you to stay.

276
00:20:48,209 --> 00:20:48,770
Fine.

277
00:20:49,209 --> 00:20:50,170
I'll go back to my room.

278
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:55,770
I'll use the front door.

279
00:21:22,969 --> 00:21:23,690
(Since I'm here,)

280
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:25,690
(I might as well make things clear.)

281
00:21:34,449 --> 00:21:35,089
- I...
- I...

282
00:21:38,449 --> 00:21:39,024
You go first.

283
00:21:41,890 --> 00:21:43,249
I have something to say.

284
00:21:43,690 --> 00:21:45,010
