00:37:41,850 --> 00:37:42,810
I'll do what you say

574
00:37:43,130 --> 00:37:44,010
and take care of myself.

575
00:37:45,010 --> 00:37:45,810
In a few days,

576
00:37:46,409 --> 00:37:47,330
I will go to Zhiyi.

577
00:37:47,969 --> 00:37:49,689
Please continue treating me then.

578
00:38:10,090 --> 00:38:11,929
If you didn't get the grains and fodder,

579
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:16,249
many brothers would die this winter.

580
00:38:17,689 --> 00:38:19,449
I am the adviser of the Chenrong Army.

581
00:38:19,889 --> 00:38:21,729
I'm doing what I should.

582
00:38:23,090 --> 00:38:23,929
How did you

583
00:38:23,929 --> 00:38:25,570
convince the Tushan Family
to lend a hand?

584
00:38:26,249 --> 00:38:29,449
Just do it as the businessman does.

585
00:38:31,570 --> 00:38:34,130
What business could make them take risks
to provide us

586
00:38:34,169 --> 00:38:36,010
(Hong Jiang)
with grains and fodder for free?

587
00:38:40,530 --> 00:38:42,050
The King of Xiyan might send people

588
00:38:42,050 --> 00:38:43,090
to inspect Qingshui Town.

589
00:38:43,290 --> 00:38:44,969
Tell our people to be cautious

590
00:38:45,649 --> 00:38:46,489
lest we're exposed.

591
00:38:48,010 --> 00:38:48,729
Why?

592
00:38:49,689 --> 00:38:51,530
Could they find out
about the grain supply?

593
00:38:52,050 --> 00:38:53,409
With Tushan Jing's capability,

594
00:38:55,489 --> 00:38:57,610
I don't think he can't handle it well.

595
00:38:59,570 --> 00:39:00,449
Then what happened?

596
00:39:06,370 --> 00:39:08,649
If you don't want to say,
you surely have your reasons.

597
00:39:08,810 --> 00:39:10,010
I won't ask you.

598
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:12,370
I will instruct soldiers

599
00:39:12,689 --> 00:39:14,249
to act cautiously.

600
00:39:29,072 --> 00:39:30,409
(Why not quit being a princess)

601
00:39:31,530 --> 00:39:32,770
and rove the world with me?

602
00:39:48,649 --> 00:39:49,328
Okay.

603
00:39:50,050 --> 00:39:51,290
If you give up everything,

604
00:39:51,969 --> 00:39:52,770
I will go with you.

605
00:40:10,050 --> 00:40:10,810
Grandfather.

606
00:40:13,850 --> 00:40:14,610
Grandfather.

607
00:40:15,489 --> 00:40:16,530
I am back.

608
00:40:40,370 --> 00:40:41,010
Grandfather.

609
00:40:50,209 --> 00:40:51,330
You even had the nerve

610
00:40:51,330 --> 00:40:53,649
to call off the wedding
in front of everyone.

611
00:40:54,050 --> 00:40:56,249
I thought you were afraid of nothing.

612
00:41:02,530 --> 00:41:03,610
Come out and talk.

613
00:41:07,610 --> 00:41:08,370
Come out.

614
00:41:15,090 --> 00:41:16,209
What exactly is going on

615
00:41:16,770 --> 00:41:18,449
between you and Fangfeng Bei?

616
00:41:19,330 --> 00:41:20,570
If he wants to marry you,

617
00:41:21,010 --> 00:41:23,249
will he have no courage to meet us?

618
00:41:24,449 --> 00:41:25,689
Fangfeng Bei is dead.

619
00:41:28,489 --> 00:41:30,610
Are you sure Fangfeng Bei is dead?

620
00:41:31,530 --> 00:41:32,169
I am sure.

621
00:41:33,729 --> 00:41:35,449
Fangfeng Bei

622
00:41:36,889 --> 00:41:38,489
will never appear again.

623
00:41:42,530 --> 00:41:44,729
Fangfeng Bei died for me.

624
00:41:45,810 --> 00:41:47,130
I don't want to talk

625
00:41:48,810 --> 00:41:49,889
about him anymore.

626
00:41:50,169 --> 00:41:51,610
In front of the crowds,

627
00:41:51,929 --> 00:41:54,249
Fangfeng Bei and Xiaoyao left together.

628
00:41:54,729 --> 00:41:56,209
Now Xiaoyao has come back,

629
00:41:56,649 --> 00:41:57,570
but he is dead.

630
00:41:58,130 --> 00:42:00,370
We owe an explanation to the people.

631
00:42:10,929 --> 00:42:12,610
When my guards caught up with Xiaoyao,

632
00:42:12,610 --> 00:42:13,850
Fangfeng Bei refused to release her.

633
00:42:14,370 --> 00:42:15,649
To protect the princess,

634
00:42:15,649 --> 00:42:16,449
the guards killed him

635
00:42:16,449 --> 00:42:17,850
in an emergency.

636
00:42:18,130 --> 00:42:20,010
Actually, it's good
that Fangfeng Bei was killed.

637
00:42:20,649 --> 00:42:21,770
That's what the Chishui Family

638
00:42:21,770 --> 00:42:23,130
and other people want.

639
00:42:23,649 --> 00:42:26,249
It also helps appease Fenglong
and Chenrong Yi.

640
00:42:26,489 --> 00:42:28,449
The Fangfeng Family doesn't dare
to complain

641
00:42:29,130 --> 00:42:30,010
because of a baseborn son.

642
00:42:30,610 --> 00:42:31,729
That's good.

643
00:42:40,249 --> 00:42:41,370
You go back and rest.

644
00:42:42,130 --> 00:42:44,729
I need to discuss some things
with Grandfather.

645
00:42:52,249 --> 00:42:52,770
You may leave.

646
00:43:06,736 --> 00:43:08,489
When you asked me
to persuade Xiang Liu to surrender,

647
00:43:08,570 --> 00:43:09,570
did you already know

648
00:43:09,570 --> 00:43:11,050
that Xiang Liu and Fangfeng Bei

649
00:43:11,409 --> 00:43:12,330
were the same person?

650
00:43:15,649 --> 00:43:17,689
It was just my speculation before.

651
00:43:18,770 --> 00:43:20,850
I only found it out today.

652
00:43:27,889 --> 00:43:30,249
If it had not been
for Chi Chen back then,

653
00:43:31,449 --> 00:43:32,449
Auntie wouldn't have...

654
00:43:35,169 --> 00:43:37,489
Xiang Liu is really too arrogant.

655
00:43:38,370 --> 00:43:40,489
How dare he see Xiaoyao again.

656
00:44:02,179 --> 00:44:05,411
♪Looking back on my old days♪

657
00:44:06,697 --> 00:44:10,979
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

658
00:44:13,059 --> 00:44:17,859
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

659
00:44:20,995 --> 00:44:23,267
♪Only emptiness remained♪

660
00:44:26,211 --> 00:44:29,283
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

661
00:44:31,132 --> 00:44:35,523
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

662
00:44:37,059 --> 00:44:42,532
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

663
00:44:43,483 --> 00:44:49,315
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

664
00:44:52,163 --> 00:44:56,899
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

665
00:44:58,211 --> 00:45:02,723
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

666
00:45:04,163 --> 00:45:10,115
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

667
00:45:10,892 --> 00:45:15,203
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

668
00:45:16,195 --> 00:45:21,161
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

669
00:45:22,153 --> 00:45:26,761
♪All is bleak without you♪

670
00:45:28,099 --> 00:45:33,705
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

671
00:45:34,819 --> 00:45:45,833
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
